Gimli is a fictional character from J. R. R. Tolkien 's Middle-earth legendarium , featured in The Lord of the Rings .
A dwarf warrior , he is the son of Gl√≥in -LRB- a character from Tolkien 's earlier novel , The Hobbit -RRB- .
Gimli is chosen to represent the race of Dwarves in the Fellowship of the Ring .
As such , he is one of the primary characters of the novel .
In the course of the adventure , Gimli aids the Ring-bearer , participates in the War of the Ring , and becomes close friends with Legolas , overcoming an ancient enmity of Dwarves and Elves .